### English localisation for VG Examine System

### General examine strings

examine-name = [bold]{ $name }[/bold]
examine-name-selfaware = [bold]You[/bold]

examine-can-see = Looking at { OBJECT($ent) }, you see:
examine-can-see-selfaware = Looking at yourself, you see:
examine-can-see-nothing = { CAPITALIZE(SUBJECT($ent)) } is completely naked.
examine-can-see-nothing-selfaware = You are completely naked.

